# Environment variables for the TTB Label Verification Tool.
#
# Copy to `.env` (which is gitignored) and fill in as needed.
# NEVER commit real secrets — `.env` is ignored on purpose.
#
# This app is fully LOCAL (Tesseract OCR, no cloud APIs) and needs NO secrets
# to run. The entries below only apply if you wire up optional integrations:

# Deploy only — Render API key, used by scripts/deploy_render.sh. Do not commit.
# RENDER_API_KEY=

# Optional override if a cloud OCR/vision backend is ever added. Do not commit.
# OCR_API_KEY=
